{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PaymentIntentProvider"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"PaymentIntentProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" enables delayed payment intent creation, allowing you to defer","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the creation of a payment intent until just before payment confirmation or when it is required.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When using ","type":"text"},{"code":"Session","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" with a payment intent provider instead of a pre-created intent,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the SDK will call ","type":"text"},{"code":"createPaymentIntent()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" asynchronously when needed. The provider","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"must also supply the basic payment information (amount, currency, customerId) synchronously.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Usage Example","anchor":"Usage-Example"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class MyPaymentIntentProvider: NSObject, PaymentIntentProvider {","    let amount: NSDecimalNumber = NSDecimalNumber(string: \"99.99\")","    let currency: String = \"USD\"","    let customerId: String? = \"customer_123\"","","    func createPaymentIntent() async throws -> AWXPaymentIntent {","        \/\/ Call your backend to create the payment intent","        let response = try await MyBackendAPI.createPaymentIntent(","            amount: amount.decimalValue,","            currency: currency,","            customerId: customerId","        )","        return response.paymentIntent","    }","}","","\/\/ Use with Session","let provider = MyPaymentIntentProvider()","let session = Session(","    paymentIntentProvider: provider,","    countryCode: \"US\",","    returnURL: \"myapp:\/\/payment\/return\"",")"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Important Notes","anchor":"Important-Notes"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"amount"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"currency"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customerId"},{"type":"text","text":" properties must return values immediately (they cannot be async)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The values returned by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"amount"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"currency"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customerId"},{"type":"text","text":" must match the values"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AWXPaymentIntent"},{"type":"text","text":" returned by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"createPaymentIntent()"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"code":"amount","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" should be zero for recurring-only payments (no immediate charge)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":"createPaymentIntent()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method will only be called once, and the result is cached","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"createPaymentIntent()"},{"text":" throws an error, the payment flow will fail","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"code":"Sessio